TO: BARBARA EPSTEIN

CC, 1 p.





Montreux, Nov. 8, 1965

Palace Hotel

Dear Barbara,

Many thanks for your very kind telegram.

I am now sending you a copy of my article (entitled Appendix 3) dealing with the various reviews of my EO, and especially with Edmund Wilson's.

